81u/poem-6ydbZ6DYIAXdXPOo7-jSqg">Nam triều - 南朝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-x%C3%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-D%C4%A9nh-ph%C3%B3-T%E1%BB%81-ch%C3%A2u-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-qVWyTld7t0sMWVWht6Iolw">Tống xá đệ Dĩnh phó Tề châu kỳ 1 - 送舍弟頻赴齊州其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-m%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-pfuUA7uGS4qURp0ZBic0fA">Tuyệt cú mạn hứng kỳ 5 - 絕句漫興其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/%E1%BB%A8c-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-ni%C3%AAn/poem-D7kAh77xitVChfISTI47fQ">Ức đắc nhị thập niên - 憶得二十年</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
